data.description: Welcome to your new desert home, nestled on a 6,970 sq ft elevated lot that reveals stunning views of the whole valley and its mountains. An incredible 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and 1598 sqft home located on Cuando Way, just a short drive from downtown Palm Springs or the village of Desert Hot Springs.For AirBnB investors, this home has a fantastic track record. Best in class Short Term Vacation Rental with a great reputation and SuperHost status. Sold optionally furnished turnkey, ready to book with current bookings. This is a top of the line home with high quality features, a location with views for miles and a tranquil setting with open desert hills east and Mt San Jacinto to the west. The views are exhilarating from this modern and fun styled home located hundreds of feet above the Coachella Valley floor in Miracle Heights neighborhood. This is a custom built home that provides the best in luxury and comfort. Enter through front door and inside to soaring cathedral ceilings and an open floor plan. The entire home has been well maintained with a new appliances and drought tolerant landscaping. Outside, the enormous covered patio gives you outdoor living room space beside the fire pit seating areas that seem hung against the majestic mountain backdrop. Meticulous attention to details and numerous amenities have been thought of and put into place for a fabulous guest experience and low owner maintenance.Quiet, established neighborhood with nearby mineral springs, which gives the city its nickname of Spa City as well as draws visitors. Neighborhood is home to desirable Palm Springs Unified School District. Close to nearby restaurants, markets, and shopping.
